                "query": "You are a professional marketing copywriter for an Indian MSME. \ninput data {{step_1}}\nBased on this raw message: \"{{step_1['message']}}\" and Target Segment: \"{{step_1['segment']}}\", generate a high-converting email.\nYour response MUST be a JSON object with exactly these two keys:\n1. \"subject\": A catchy, short subject line with an emoji.\n2. \"body\": A professional, responsive HTML email body. Use a clean design with a purple header (#4f46e5), clear call-to-action, and professional sign-off. Do NOT use markdown code blocks (```html), just give the raw HTML string.",
